{
  "stem": "25288.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Just when we heard something-- I heard this and I  heard-- we didn't know nothing about what was going on.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we were in-- somewhere in Russia, we were loading-- that was in early '44.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In a railroad station, we were loading railroad cars with long logs.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And a train came in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Soldiers, Hungarian soldiers, came back from vacation, came back.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they told us they deported the Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We didn't believe them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We didn't know anything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We didn't believe them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Then other people came back from Hungary, other soldiers.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Then this must be true.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We heard the word Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "What is Auschwitz?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We didn't know anything about this Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Then we found out it's true.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Going back to before the war, did you or any  of your brothers and sisters marry?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't understand.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Was what?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Married?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, married.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Married.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My brother and my two sisters were married before the war.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my brother was married.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Yeah, they had children.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My older sister had three children.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My brother had two.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my younger sister-- she was married to-- well, six, seven years.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she had one child-- five years little boy.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Five year old.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we had the business [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We continued just the same.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were worrying always, worrying.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we didn't know really anything what was going  on.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Just from the papers, from the papers, that's what we knew.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we knew not everything was true what the papers said.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we know there is something else going on from what the papers says.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we were worrying, always worrying what is going to happen.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we didn't dream it was going to be a Holocaust, the Jewish people were going to be taken to concentration camps.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We didn't dream about that.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
